## The mental model in one diagram

```
Deployment config (set via API):
  default:    [v1 100%]
  canary:     [v1 50%, v2 50%]
  enterprise: [v1 100%]

Request arrives:
  Override header? ──► exact version, done
  Cohort header?   ──► use that cohort's pool
  Nothing?         ──► use default pool
          │
          ▼
  Version-Key header? ──► deterministic pick from pool
  Nothing?            ──► random weighted pick from pool
          │
          ▼
  Request hits correct version of your Worker
  ctx.version tells you how it got there
```
